viceroy resourc corp detail gold assay viceroy resourc corp said recent drill on the lesley ann deposit extend the high-grad miner over a width of 600 feet . assay rang from about 0.35 ounc of gold per short ton over a 150-foot interv at a depth of 350 to 500 feet to about 1.1 ounc of gold per ton over a 65-foot interv at a depth of 200 to 410 feet .